    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape. It runs super smoothly and has been well-loved and cared for. It's the perfect companion for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
