      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 powerhouse. This 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, which has been recently overhauled with Beisan systems components for optimal phase timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been proactively addressed with a subframe reinforcement kit to mitigate floor pan fatigue. Suspension remains tight with refreshed RTABs and FCABs, maintaining the sharp turn-in characteristic of the E46 platform. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a recent rod bearing service. This is a visceral, analog machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable engine. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free environment with premium upholstery that remains soft and supportive. Every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that feels as strong as the day it left the lot. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection, ensuring it is ready for its next owner with no immediate work required. This is a solid, reliable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies a superior balance of mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. This unit has been maintained to a commendable standard, ensuring reliable performance and a sophisticated presence on the road. Having undergone a thorough assessment to verify its operational readiness, this automobile represents a compelling acquisition for those seeking a high-caliber driving experience without compromise. We invite you to experience the refined quality and enduring value of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more miles of memories! It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for. If you're looking for a dependable car that looks great and won't let you down, this is the one. Come by and take it for a test drive\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This flat-six M96-powered coupe delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance is documented, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a dry rear main seal. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the communicative steering feedback synonymous with the 911 lineage. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its history, the drivetrain is robust and the cooling system has been optimized with a low-temp thermostat and aluminum radiators. A high-performance, driver-focused example ready for the circuit or the canyon.",
